  questionnaire application. The agent systematically tested the application
  through the browser, covering the questionnaire flow, report generation, PDF
  download, admin login, and various API endpoints. During testing, it
  identified minor issues such as ESLint warnings, an outdated page title, and
  confirmed the correct functioning of form validation and API authentication.
  After providing a detailed summary of its findings, the agent proceeded to fix
  these issues. It implemented 8 atomic commits, addressing schema updates,
  enhancing form sections (Daytime and Mental Health), improving the
  comprehensive sleep analysis in the report and PDF generation, updating mock
  data, refining the CSV export, and correcting the application's page title and
  description. The  directory was intentionally left untracked
  as it contains IDE-specific configuration.
